{"tid":1669852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2016香港9位警察曾到台灣押解水泥封屍案疑犯回港","createTime":"2019-10-22T20:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T09:46:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":800,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"c22ed992f0f330b1b82a21fd33ea7e0e070097a0","tid":1669852,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:13:00.000Z","msg":"李羽蝶 報導  / 桃園市<br />\n<br />\n香港「水泥封屍案」3名嫌犯劉錫豪、曾祥欣、張善恒，潛逃台灣躲藏30天。昨(11日)3人落網，今(12日)由香港警方派來台灣的9名警察，陪同搭乘班機，押解回香港。而香港警方與刑事局人員在空橋內完成交接程序，直接搭乘國泰航空CX467班機離開。<br />\n<br />\n由於他們所搭乘的國泰航空是屬於香港國籍航空公司，機艙內的管轄權屬於香港警方，所以台港警方才會在空橋內完成交接程序，這也是雙方首次在桃園機場空橋移交犯罪嫌疑人。(翻攝網路)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/society/201604/201604121740223.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Fsociety%2F201604%2F201604121740223.html&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=e7a77b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/society/201604/201604121740223.html</a>"},{"pid":"4019a7e0f934446d16d7665cc0fffbe753b63020","tid":1669852,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:13:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158b21c425508c5cb9ddabb3f118783d922c8905","tid":1669852,"uid":27319,"like":277,"dislike":1,"score":276,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:14:49.000Z","msg":"今次其實都可以喺機場禁區移交逃犯"},{"pid":"0217a54f2d3da3e12df618529ef0b9a6830987a3","tid":1669852,"uid":112581,"like":500,"dislike":2,"score":498,"quote":{"pid":"158b21c425508c5cb9ddabb3f118783d922c8905","tid":1669852,"uid":27319,"like":277,"dislike