ore":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:02:39.000Z","msg":"蘋果：<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員涂謹申表示，外地執法人員不能在港執法，但外地人員可在當事人同意，並在香港警員陪同下見面，屬一般「面見證人」程序。而粗略統計過去10年，本港已有多達數百宗「面見證人」安排。涂相信，陳同佳明日獲釋後，台灣警員可與陳會面，確認陳是否自願赴台投案。而香港警方徵詢陳意願後，可在就近警署等地點會面，當確定陳身份和案情細節，以及是否自願赴台投案，再了解其離港時間和航班後，並陪同陳登機，隨後台方在機上對陳進行押解。"},{"pid":"5ea9956459ab8f6774147eb3ea832752dd5d13da","tid":1669852,"uid":112467,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"5f2f691c9914ddd63454cbc37c2ff6a22ac4413d","tid":1669852,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0a7999b442a89b1766c372308cf80671764c64a2","tid":1669852,"uid":112467,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:45:35.000Z","msg":"理論上用返呢次做法都得嘅<br />\n台灣派人坐長榮嚟 空橋交人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04be4fa98c7581f61c93e21f9ecee081c6a3ebd8","tid":1669852,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0217a54f2d3da3e12df618529ef0b9a6830987a3","tid":1669852,"uid":112581,"like":500,"dislike":2,"score":498,"quote":{"pid":"158b21c425508c5cb9ddabb3f118783d922c8905","tid":1669852,"uid":27319,"like":277,"dislike":1,"score":276,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:14:49.000Z","msg":"今次其實都可以喺機場禁區移交逃犯"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:17:25.000Z","msg":"做左咪即係認逃犯條例根本冇必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然話港人港審最好<br />\n不過香港自己放棄自己審怪得邊個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:08:10.000Z","msg":"犯案地點係台灣<br />\n要跟返台灣法律審"},{"pid":"397d47e82a707de8b031dc5b244d36345f6a8cea","tid":1669852,"uid":106051,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:08:16.000Z","msg":"冇可能嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林太話咁樣會損害司法嫁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"