「外國」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"5e2234e892c1791c50bacd7d47c81e7db129fa33","tid":1669852,"uid":120629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:38:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a48fb2599d013c3af475eb0315debc1802578f2","tid":1669852,"uid":116459,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c22ed992f0f330b1b82a21fd33ea7e0e070097a0","tid":1669852,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:13:00.000Z","msg":"李羽蝶 報導  / 桃園市<br />\n<br />\n香港「水泥封屍案」3名嫌犯劉錫豪、曾祥欣、張善恒，潛逃台灣躲藏30天。昨(11日)3人落網，今(12日)由香港警方派來台灣的9名警察，陪同搭乘班機，押解回香港。而香港警方與刑事局人員在空橋內完成交接程序，直接搭乘國泰航空CX467班機離開。<br />\n<br />\n由於他們所搭乘的國泰航空是屬於香港國籍航空公司，機艙內的管轄權屬於香港警方，所以台港警方才會在空橋內完成交接程序，這也是雙方首次在桃園機場空橋移交犯罪嫌疑人。(翻攝網路)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/society/201604/201604121740223.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Fsociety%2F201604%2F201604121740223.html&d=tlSH0trWbW1MAbtCTa3DU6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=e7a77b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/society/201604/201604121740223.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:42:49.000Z","msg":"香港國藉航空公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14eb21b9170650dfcb016740bfdfeb9c94b53a3","tid":1669852,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35b32fb1bb72888a7cb5f0374d7624ce13116586","tid":1669852,"uid":2126,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"6328b24d3f320ac44e1a63e974f824c10ccb06ba","tid":1669852,"uid":38891,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"de518133319fb961a1df58d6a2ef3e16a1ec9df8","tid":1669852,"uid":165683,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:21:16.000Z","msg":"但禁就變左合理化未來移交比中國<br />\n我反對"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:23:58.000Z","msg":"只要台灣話一定死刑<br />\n不過可以比香港自己審<br />\n陳同佳一定唔會去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"c